Package: americanRoulette
Title: Shiny R American Roulette App
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: person("Ignat", "Kulinka", email = "ignatkulinka@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: American Roulette is an R Shiny implementation of the popular 
  casino game, roulette. During the game, the player/user can click on the 
  plot of the roulette betting table to place bets. In addition, the user 
  can use provided CPU bet generator to help with the bet selection. The 
  application supports bet editing as well as game-session review with helful 
  plots and graphics. Lastly, all of the useful data generated can be exported
  and downloaded for further analysis.
URL: https://github.com/ignatkulinka/americanRoulette
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
  ggthemes, 
  ggplot2,
  DT,
  shiny
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
